Package: oneway
Title: One-Way Statistical Analyses
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Joon-Keat", "Lai", , "p10911004@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9840-5836"))
Description: An integrated toolkit for one-way statistical analyses. The package 
             implements a collection of methods for one-way experimental designs, 
             including tests of assumptions (normality and homoscedasticity), 
             one-way analysis of variance, robust and nonparametric alternatives, 
             multiple comparison procedures, effect size estimators, confidence 
             intervals, and descriptive summaries. Functions are designed with a 
             consistent interface to support reproducible and user-friendly 
             statistical workflows.
